---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="Terms of use for China Buyer Prep."
  canonical="/terms/"
>
  <section class="content-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
      <p>These terms apply when you use China Buyer Prep guides, checklists, and resource pages.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>General information</h2>
      <p>China Buyer Prep provides practical preparation information for travel, Canton Fair planning, and sourcing research. Content is for general educational use and is not legal, financial, immigration, or purchasing advice.</p>

      <h2>Verify before acting</h2>
      <p>Requirements for visas, payments, travel, trade fairs, suppliers, and shipping can change. Always confirm important decisions with official sources, service providers, or qualified professionals before booking or buying.</p>

      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>Some pages may link to external resources. We are not responsible for the content, policies, or availability of external websites.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have a question about these terms, contact us through the <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
